      <div class="text-6xl font-semibold">Kang</div>
      <hr class="w-80 h-2 my-4 border-0 md:my-5 bg-neutral-800" />
      <div class="pb-5 text-4xl font-medium">Software / Machine Learning</div>
      <div class="text-2xl font-extralight">
        Experienced Software Engineer and Entrepreneur with a Bachelor's in
        Computer Engineering and a Master's in Natural Language Processing
      </div>
      <div class="social-icons flex sticky pt-10 -ml-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/tkang7"
          target="_blank"
          class="mx-3"
          aria-label="Github"
          title="Github"
